(3390, 'Agatha Christie\'s Poirot', 'Baseado na obra de Agatha Christie, a série acompanha as aventuras do detetive belga Hercule Poirot, que tenta desvendar casos de misteriosos assassinatos.', '[\'Crime\', \'Drama\', \'Mistério\']', 'tv', '1989-01-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6f4IVfbn8knb7RjdZlGLuW5guDc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jB3CQHS4zBzD00yZG936WmsH6P4.jpg', NULL, 13, 790),
